etymology.interpretation: 李旭婷 is a Chinese personal name consisting of the surname 李 (Lǐ) and the given name 旭婷 (Xùtíng). The name suggests qualities associated with dawn and grace.

examples.pinyin: Lǐ Xùtíng shì wǒ de hǎo péngyǒu.
examples.english: Li Xuting is my good friend.

examples.chinese: 我给李旭婷发了一条短信(我給李旭婷發了一條短信)。
examples.pinyin: Wǒ gěi Lǐ Xùtíng fā le yī tiáo duǎnxìn.
examples.english: I sent a text message to Li Xuting.

examples.chinese: 李旭婷和我们一起去旅行(李旭婷和我們一起去旅行)。
examples.pinyin: Lǐ Xùtíng hé wǒmen yīqǐ qù lǚxíng.
examples.english: Li Xuting is going on a trip with us.
